title: Opposing 'intentional destruction of human life,' 70 people protest Planned Parenthood
text: She and others held candles and signs outside the clinic on W. Michigan Avenue hours after a similarly sized group left with their pro-choice, pro-Planned Parenthood posters and pink hats.
